---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 171
By: John Smith the Platonist
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Volition, Obedience and Conformity=Intention
Reference:
  Title: John
  Location: VII 17
---
He (Christ) hangs all true acquaintance with divinity upon the doing
God's will. ‘If any man will do his will, he shall know of the
doctrine, whether it be of God’.
